Create the folder structure for tidyGWAS

setup_pipeline_paths.Rd

Create the folder structure for tidyGWAS

Usage

setup_pipeline_paths(outdir, filename)

Arguments

outdir

output directory

filename

filename for the raw sumstats

Value

a list of filepaths

Examples

setup_pipeline_paths(tempfile())
